What’s that, Shelley?

130
00:05:39,470 --> 00:05:40,830
I see.

131
00:05:40,830 --> 00:05:43,930
Steve Bannon is not a fan of late nineties
rock music.

132
00:05:43,930 --> 00:05:47,159
He just meant aggressive and confrontational.

133
00:05:47,159 --> 00:05:49,969
